<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>ولُّوا <span class="c2">(٥)</span> فلما رَجَونا عدلَهُمْ ظلموا <span class="c2">(٦)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
